			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Gloria Dyc</strong></span>&rsquo;s work has appeared in <em>Prairie Schooner</em>, <em>South Dakota Review</em>, and <em>Sing Heavenly Muse</em>. She recently edited <em>Wanbli Ho</em>, a literary journal featuring Native American and high plains writers. She lives in Continental Divide, New Mexico.</p><a href="/contributors/gloria-dyc" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
